          "Expected to replace unreachable terminator with conditional branch.");
-  auto CondBr =
-      State.Builder.CreateCondBr(ConditionBit, State.CFG.PrevBB, nullptr);
+  // Create a conditional branch with temporary valid successors (the current
+  // block) so IRBuilder has non-null destinations. They will be cleared and
+  // connected later when the successor blocks are created.
